          <li><a href={url("/case-studies/knaut-boston")}>Harvard SiV Boston-metro loop</a> — the matter-qubit-memory counterpart on similar metro-scale deployed fibre.</li>
          <li><a href={url("/case-studies/delft-three-node")}>Delft NV three-node network</a> — the academic three-node entanglement-and-swap reference, on shorter fibre.</li>
          <li><a href={url("/case-studies/epb")}>EPB Quantum Network</a> — the other entanglement-based US deployment, also using Qunnect hardware.</li>
